vulnerability.name: USN-6129-2
vulnerability.description: USN-6129-1 fixed a vulnerability in Avahi. This update provides the corresponding update for Ubuntu 14.04 LTS, Ubuntu 16.04 LTS and Ubuntu 18.04 LTS.  Original advisory details:   It was discovered that Avahi incorrectly handled certain DBus messages. A  local attacker could possibly use this issue to cause Avahi to crash,  resulting in a denial of service.

statements.status_notes: Avahi could be made to crash if it received specially crafted DBus traffic. Available with Ubuntu Pro.
